WEBVTT

00:16.390 --> 00:17.920
Just as Your Highness suspected,

00:17.920 --> 00:18.870
there is indeed a mysterious person

00:18.870 --> 00:20.870
who is not on the delegation's list.

00:32.150 --> 00:32.670
Plus,

00:32.670 --> 00:34.670
with several experts
protecting the Eagle King,

00:34.670 --> 00:36.600
it's hard for us to force our way in.

00:37.350 --> 00:39.710
What has the Eagle King been doing
these past few days?

00:39.710 --> 00:40.710
Nothing unusual.

00:41.470 --> 00:43.110
The officials of the Ministry of Rites
took them to visit

00:43.110 --> 00:44.380
the East and West Markets.

00:44.380 --> 00:45.150
They also went to the martial arts arena

00:45.150 --> 00:46.840
to train the Northern Qin warriors
in horseback archery.

00:46.840 --> 00:47.470
Should we

00:47.470 --> 00:49.320
find a time when the Eagle King is away

00:49.320 --> 00:50.840
to force that mysterious person out?

00:50.840 --> 00:52.880
But if he's determined not to come out,

00:52.880 --> 00:53.940
how do we force him?

00:57.390 --> 00:59.720
The delegation didn't bring many people.

01:00.070 --> 01:01.600
And during
the mounted archery tournament,

01:01.600 --> 01:03.330
the Eagle King will definitely

01:03.960 --> 01:05.960
send his three strongest fighters.

01:06.640 --> 01:07.840
If you think about it,

01:08.030 --> 01:09.510
that's when security at the Honglu Temple

01:09.510 --> 01:11.430
will be at its weakest.

01:11.840 --> 01:13.150
Do you mean

01:13.950 --> 01:15.210
creating a diversion?

01:17.640 --> 01:19.840
No. We strike while they're distracted.

01:19.840 --> 01:20.710
However,

01:24.280 --> 01:26.610
we still need one more pawn
to make it work.

02:52.570 --> 02:56.560
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:57.100 --> 02:59.570
[Episode 10]

03:22.040 --> 03:24.770
♪ One glance stirs heart's doom,
near yet far ♪

03:24.000 --> 03:24.990
Hurry, pack it up.

03:24.990 --> 03:27.540
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

03:29.240 --> 03:33.250
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

03:33.420 --> 03:35.420
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

03:37.380 --> 03:40.380
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

03:40.790 --> 03:45.160
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

03:45.750 --> 03:48.660
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

03:49.590 --> 03:52.410
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

03:54.070 --> 03:58.280
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

04:21.510 --> 04:22.170
Don't move.

04:40.360 --> 04:41.000
Done.

04:50.000 --> 04:51.600
If you really make it in time,

04:51.830 --> 04:53.760
I'll agree to have a match with Yao.

04:56.510 --> 04:59.570
The winner will lead the Beifu soldiers
onto the field.

05:09.900 --> 05:12.030
Remember to warm yourself by the fire.

05:12.360 --> 05:13.420
Don't catch a cold.

05:40.680 --> 05:42.950
You are brilliant, Young Master Yao!

05:42.950 --> 05:43.870
Awesome! So accurate!

05:43.870 --> 05:46.800
You are brilliant, Young Master Yao!

05:50.960 --> 05:52.640
See? I told you it would work.

05:53.120 --> 05:54.680
As long as Anmin's injured left leg

05:54.680 --> 05:55.680
is fixed to the stirrup,

05:55.680 --> 05:57.000
he can still control
the horse's direction,

05:57.000 --> 05:58.430
and it's even more stable.

05:58.430 --> 05:59.800
This is too ugly.

05:59.870 --> 06:01.310
Can good looks feed you?

06:01.720 --> 06:02.270
Besides,

06:02.270 --> 06:04.000
I stayed up all night making this.

06:04.000 --> 06:05.330
Look at my dark circles.

06:06.360 --> 06:07.760
Anmin, what do you think?

06:10.920 --> 06:11.750
General Xiao,

06:12.430 --> 06:13.600
can I still fight?

06:18.240 --> 06:19.240
Bring the horses.

06:19.590 --> 06:20.650
Let's have a match.

06:21.190 --> 06:22.990
If you win, I'll let you compete.

06:25.510 --> 06:27.920
Lady Xie, I owe you a favor.

06:28.750 --> 06:30.600
If you need anything in the future,

06:30.600 --> 06:32.000
as long as it
doesn't violate the laws of Ye,

06:32.000 --> 06:33.159
I will definitely help you.

06:33.159 --> 06:34.970
Okay, I'll remember this favor.

06:35.210 --> 06:36.810
I'll come to you for it later.

06:51.870 --> 06:52.800
Sister Yuanji,

06:54.430 --> 06:58.490
you were the one who asked someone
to invite the Dowager Princess, right?

06:59.800 --> 07:01.360
Why did you help Anmin?

07:02.160 --> 07:04.250
Because we are friends.

07:06.200 --> 07:07.080
Friends?

07:12.750 --> 07:13.430
Friends.

07:14.830 --> 07:16.090
Don't misunderstand.

07:16.560 --> 07:17.890
He is not my sweetheart.

07:18.270 --> 07:19.670
Neither is His Highness.

07:20.000 --> 07:21.510
Between men and women in this world,

07:21.510 --> 07:23.310
there is not only romantic love.

07:23.750 --> 07:25.190
There can also be camaraderie

07:25.190 --> 07:26.450
and close friendship.

07:26.870 --> 07:28.130
I appreciate Xiao Yao,

07:28.160 --> 07:29.890
just as I appreciate Xiao Wuyi.

07:30.000 --> 07:31.750
But neither of them is romantic love.

07:31.750 --> 07:34.159
Is there any difference between the two?

07:34.750 --> 07:36.240
Friends and confidants

07:36.680 --> 07:37.600
can share joys

07:37.600 --> 07:38.600
and sorrows.

07:39.600 --> 07:40.560
But couples

07:40.590 --> 07:42.990
must become each other's joys and sorrows.

07:43.950 --> 07:44.800
My husband

07:46.510 --> 07:48.110
has been gone for a long time.

07:49.980 --> 07:50.620
Sister,

07:50.950 --> 07:51.950
I always feel that

07:52.240 --> 07:53.270
Xiao Wuyi didn't kill

07:53.270 --> 07:54.630
your Mr. Runheng.

07:54.920 --> 07:55.830
How do you know?

07:56.870 --> 07:58.800
Just like how the Dowager Princess

07:58.800 --> 08:01.000
didn't want Anmin
to go to the battlefield,

08:01.000 --> 08:02.190
Xiao Wuyi doesn't seem to care

08:02.190 --> 08:03.600
about what others think of him.

08:03.600 --> 08:05.480
He just focuses on his own business.

08:05.480 --> 08:06.950
So if you want to know the truth,

08:06.950 --> 08:08.390
you might as well ask him directly.

08:08.390 --> 08:09.800
It's true that he acts ruthlessly,

08:09.800 --> 08:11.510
but he is definitely magnanimous.

08:11.510 --> 08:13.750
Jiayu, how could I not know?

08:14.230 --> 08:15.710
But the truth for me

08:15.750 --> 08:17.150
might be even more cruel.

08:18.040 --> 08:19.360
Xiao Wuyi's silence

08:19.630 --> 08:21.160
is exactly his generosity.

08:22.070 --> 08:25.130
Isn't that just letting good people
suffer in silence?

08:48.080 --> 08:50.240
General Xiao, how is it?

09:12.150 --> 09:13.680
Greetings, Your Highness.

09:15.200 --> 09:17.000
I didn't expect you to be here.

09:17.870 --> 09:20.120
I have had doubts in my heart for years.

09:20.790 --> 09:22.920
Today, after being reminded by Jiayu,

09:23.550 --> 09:25.240
I would like you to clear my doubts.

09:25.240 --> 09:26.030
What doubts?

09:26.550 --> 09:29.200
Why did you send people
to find Pei Runheng

09:30.270 --> 09:31.480
back then?

09:34.240 --> 09:35.550
Go get the envelope

09:35.960 --> 09:37.910
in the second drawer
of the cabinet next to my desk.

09:37.910 --> 09:38.440
Yes.

09:43.440 --> 09:45.720
I originally wanted to
send someone to tell him

09:45.720 --> 09:48.320
that this engagement
was only for provisions.

09:49.390 --> 09:50.650
When the time is right,

09:51.150 --> 09:52.410
I will grant your wish.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.900
Unfortunately, I was a step too late.

10:07.560 --> 10:09.020
Thank you, Your Highness.

10:10.200 --> 10:10.870
Thank you.

10:11.840 --> 10:12.480
Wait.

10:13.510 --> 10:14.510
You just said

10:15.200 --> 10:17.000
that you were reminded by Jiayu?

10:19.670 --> 10:20.440
She said

10:21.240 --> 10:22.840
that concealing this matter

10:23.000 --> 10:24.660
and refusing to seek the truth

10:25.480 --> 10:28.010
means letting good people
suffer in silence.

10:28.510 --> 10:30.630
Who doesn't she think is a good person?

10:30.630 --> 10:32.960
Jiayu is pure-hearted,

10:33.750 --> 10:35.090
yet possesses great wisdom.

10:35.090 --> 10:36.120
In the court,

10:36.120 --> 10:37.150
great treachery resembles loyalty,

10:37.150 --> 10:38.200
and vice versa.

10:38.200 --> 10:39.630
You and Jiayu

10:39.840 --> 10:41.320
seem to be poles apart,

10:42.510 --> 10:43.200
but in fact,

10:44.720 --> 10:46.180
you are fellow travelers.

10:56.910 --> 11:00.000
Couples must become
each other's joys and sorrows.

11:03.270 --> 11:03.870
My Lady,

11:04.160 --> 11:05.760
what are you thinking about?

11:09.120 --> 11:10.510
Sister Yuanji said

11:11.230 --> 11:12.380
that friends and confidants

11:12.380 --> 11:13.910
can share joys and sorrows.

11:14.030 --> 11:15.360
But couples...

11:15.360 --> 11:18.020
They must become
each other's joys and sorrows.

11:18.510 --> 11:19.710
I didn't understand.

11:19.840 --> 11:21.600
Do you understand what it means?

11:21.600 --> 11:23.960
I grew up by your side.

11:24.550 --> 11:26.000
The only husband and wife I've ever seen

11:26.000 --> 11:28.060
are the Princess and the Grand Tutor.

11:28.600 --> 11:30.120
But now they both...

11:31.030 --> 11:32.320
I really don't know.

11:32.790 --> 11:33.720
Mother said

11:34.000 --> 11:35.910
that couples should be fellow travelers.

11:35.910 --> 11:37.200
Sister Yuanji said

11:37.200 --> 11:39.600
that couples should become
each other's joys and sorrows.

11:39.600 --> 11:40.870
I understand the joys,

11:41.320 --> 11:42.600
but why the sorrows?

11:43.320 --> 11:44.790
When two people are together,

11:44.790 --> 11:46.550
isn't happiness the most important thing?

11:46.550 --> 11:48.200
There are hundreds of
kinds of people in this world,

11:48.200 --> 11:50.070
so there are hundreds of kinds of couples.

11:50.070 --> 11:52.000
You don't need to care about others.

11:52.000 --> 11:53.440
You just need to ask yourself

11:53.440 --> 11:54.910
who you want to be with.

11:55.390 --> 11:56.320
You're right.

11:56.820 --> 11:58.350
Why am I overthinking this?

11:58.840 --> 12:00.300
I already have Mao anyway.

12:00.840 --> 12:01.670
Time to sleep.

12:08.630 --> 12:11.120
Wake up.

12:12.920 --> 12:14.150
Long ago, when we set out,

12:14.150 --> 12:15.610
the willows were swaying.

12:15.750 --> 12:16.960
It means

12:16.960 --> 12:18.840
recalling the time of going to war,

12:18.840 --> 12:21.170
when the willows were swaying in the wind.

12:33.030 --> 12:35.150
Yao, do you have anything to say?

12:52.600 --> 12:54.800
Do you have to let Anmin enter the arena?

12:55.320 --> 12:57.960
Can you guarantee he will be safe?

13:01.790 --> 13:04.100
Isn't it enough
that one of my sons died for you?

13:04.100 --> 13:06.220
Do you want my other son's life too?

13:07.320 --> 13:08.380
Xiao Sheng's death

13:09.150 --> 13:10.030
is on me.

13:10.630 --> 13:11.760
But Anmin's tragedy

13:13.200 --> 13:14.460
was half to protect me,

13:15.000 --> 13:16.000
and the other half

13:18.120 --> 13:19.850
was because of your cowardice.

13:21.790 --> 13:22.550
Mother!

13:23.270 --> 13:24.480
Dragging out an ignoble existence
is not truly living.

13:24.480 --> 13:25.390
Shut up!

13:28.600 --> 13:29.530
All these years,

13:30.480 --> 13:31.810
I chose to remain silent

13:32.870 --> 13:33.870
because I thought it would be

13:33.870 --> 13:35.600
better for both Mother and Yao.

13:35.750 --> 13:37.630
But now, seeing him in such pain,

13:38.720 --> 13:40.450
I can no longer sit by and watch.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.550
Father.

13:42.360 --> 13:43.120
Mother.

13:44.060 --> 13:44.700
This time,

13:45.200 --> 13:46.860
can we let Yao do what he wants?

13:47.550 --> 13:48.950
If I cannot keep him safe,

13:49.390 --> 13:51.450
you can punish me however you see fit.

14:13.970 --> 14:15.740
[The Day of the Horseback Archery Contest]

14:26.320 --> 14:27.630
The hairstyle I combed for you

14:27.630 --> 14:29.360
is the Meteor Holding the Moon.

14:29.790 --> 14:32.270
It means Your Majesty shines like a star.

14:32.790 --> 14:34.050
Meteors fade quickly.

14:34.510 --> 14:35.720
Are you cursing me?

14:38.950 --> 14:39.880
I wouldn't dare.

14:40.080 --> 14:40.880
Your Majesty!

14:42.670 --> 14:43.630
Something terrible has happened.

14:43.630 --> 14:44.750
What is it now?

14:44.750 --> 14:46.790
News just came from the martial arts arena

14:46.790 --> 14:48.600
that Xiao Wuyi didn't go today.

14:48.840 --> 14:51.600
Instead, the eldest young master,
Xiao Yao, went.

14:51.600 --> 14:53.000
What was Xiao Wuyi doing?

14:53.120 --> 14:54.320
I don't know either.

14:54.320 --> 14:55.790
I sent many people to look for him,

14:55.790 --> 14:57.250
but there is no news at all.

14:57.360 --> 14:58.320
I don't know what

14:58.320 --> 14:59.620
Xiao Wuyi is up to.

15:00.150 --> 15:01.320
What a pity.

15:03.600 --> 15:05.860
The poisoned arrow was prepared for him.

15:06.480 --> 15:07.790
If he had come today,

15:08.600 --> 15:10.130
he would have lost his life.

15:11.030 --> 15:12.790
But he managed to escape.

15:13.720 --> 15:15.670
But his brother, Xiao Yao,

15:15.670 --> 15:17.870
injured his leg for him last time,

15:18.280 --> 15:21.750
and now he's risking his life
for him again.

15:23.910 --> 15:24.720
General Feng,

15:25.200 --> 15:26.200
what should we do?

15:26.320 --> 15:27.320
How should I know?

15:27.790 --> 15:29.910
The assembly drum
has already sounded three times.

15:29.910 --> 15:31.200
Why isn't His Highness here yet?

15:31.200 --> 15:32.510
We've already sent people to look for him,

15:32.510 --> 15:33.870
but he's nowhere to be found.

15:33.870 --> 15:34.870
What should we do?

15:35.510 --> 15:37.970
Young Master Yao,
where is the Crown Prince?

15:42.270 --> 15:44.600
The Crown Prince's arrow
wound relapsed this morning.

15:44.600 --> 15:46.270
Today, at the martial arts arena,

15:46.270 --> 15:48.120
I, Xiao Yao,

15:48.440 --> 15:49.600
will lead you all to victory.

15:49.600 --> 15:51.840
That brat from the Beifu Army
doesn't even dare face us!

15:51.840 --> 15:53.300
A flattering court lackey

15:54.240 --> 15:55.790
should keep his head down

15:56.120 --> 15:57.390
and cling to scraps.

15:58.240 --> 15:59.720
An insignificant general like him

15:59.720 --> 16:01.200
is as good as dead today.

16:01.390 --> 16:07.270
Great!

16:07.510 --> 16:09.030
The Eagle King is saying this
to the Crown Prince.

16:09.030 --> 16:11.030
If the Crown Prince doesn't show up,

16:11.030 --> 16:12.690
then only Young Master Yao...

16:13.600 --> 16:14.720
You don't trust me?

16:16.120 --> 16:18.120
I... I will go find the Crown Prince.

16:23.410 --> 16:25.000
The military command is here.

16:25.000 --> 16:26.530
Beifu Army, heed the order.

16:27.600 --> 16:30.260
Those who don't obey the order
will be executed!

16:30.510 --> 16:31.080
Yes.

17:01.160 --> 17:03.720
Xiao Yao, Left Wing Commander
of the Beifu Army,

17:03.720 --> 17:04.960
awaits the Eagle King.

17:04.960 --> 17:10.440
Great!

17:11.750 --> 17:12.810
Where is Xiao Wuyi?

17:12.920 --> 17:13.920
He won't come.

17:15.270 --> 17:16.400
Your opponent is me.

17:18.310 --> 17:19.109
That's right.

17:20.000 --> 17:21.829
A crippled wretch—yes, me.

17:22.880 --> 17:23.880
But today,

17:24.510 --> 17:26.000
I'll

17:26.680 --> 17:28.270
compete with you!

17:28.550 --> 17:31.110
I don't fight crippled opponents.

17:31.440 --> 17:34.240
Go back and prepare to collect
Xiao Wuyi's corpse.

17:38.720 --> 17:39.980
What did you do to Wuyi?

17:40.350 --> 17:41.550
Then go ask him.

17:42.830 --> 17:43.960
But at this moment,

17:44.310 --> 17:46.480
you probably won't have time to ask him.

17:46.480 --> 17:47.940
Xiao Wuyi sent you to fight

17:48.110 --> 17:51.350
just to spy on the diplomatic delegation
at Honglu Temple, right?

17:51.350 --> 17:52.830
But today's Honglu Temple

17:52.860 --> 17:55.190
has already set up a trap for him.

18:10.920 --> 18:12.640
Today, not only Xiao Wuyi,

18:13.480 --> 18:15.400
but also the students he incited

18:15.590 --> 18:17.110
will be buried with him.

18:17.510 --> 18:19.110
The match begins.

18:33.510 --> 18:35.550
The poison is lethal
upon contact with blood.

18:35.550 --> 18:37.750
The Eagle King is indeed the Eagle King.

18:48.200 --> 18:50.530
What's the matter? Why are you so anxious?

18:52.350 --> 18:53.000
What?

18:54.880 --> 18:55.400
No way.

18:56.200 --> 18:57.400
I have to replace those arrows.

18:57.400 --> 18:59.510
Brother, let me go change them.

19:00.030 --> 19:00.830
I have a way.

19:03.750 --> 19:04.680
What's going on?

19:05.510 --> 19:06.750
As long as this poison touches blood,

19:06.750 --> 19:07.750
death is certain.

19:08.510 --> 19:10.570
But Xiao Yao shows no reaction at all.

19:29.590 --> 19:30.240
Da!

19:52.030 --> 19:54.160
Great! Young Master Yao is incredible!

19:54.160 --> 19:55.310
Heroic!

19:55.590 --> 19:58.160
Young Master Yao has been raised
in Jiankang for many years.

19:58.160 --> 20:00.820
His martial arts
must have been ruined long ago.

20:00.880 --> 20:01.610
Cut the crap.

20:05.920 --> 20:06.520
Watch out!

20:18.270 --> 20:20.440
If you want to defeat
the Northern Qin cavalry,

20:20.440 --> 20:21.510
there's only one secret—

20:21.510 --> 20:22.240
courage.

20:22.960 --> 20:24.020
Fearless courage.

20:43.680 --> 20:44.590
Save him quickly!

20:44.590 --> 20:45.160
Quick!

20:45.590 --> 20:46.720
Over here, quick!

20:47.510 --> 20:48.480
A tie!

20:49.720 --> 20:50.640
A tie.

20:51.200 --> 20:52.030
I didn't lose.

20:58.400 --> 20:59.860
Young Master Yao, hold on.

21:00.590 --> 21:01.440
Where is the medical officer?

21:01.440 --> 21:02.790
Medical officer, come take a look!

21:02.790 --> 21:03.270
Hurry up.

21:03.270 --> 21:04.350
The weaklings of Southern Ye

21:04.350 --> 21:05.750
have no one to fight!

21:05.750 --> 21:07.750
Lose!

21:17.590 --> 21:19.720
Your Majesty, if I am to claim victory,

21:20.070 --> 21:21.440
I shall do so with honor.

21:22.070 --> 21:23.870
There is no need for you to worry.

21:28.920 --> 21:29.350
You...

21:34.070 --> 21:34.800
Who's there?

21:36.880 --> 21:38.880
I am a maid
from the Empress Dowager's palace.

21:38.880 --> 21:41.010
I'm here to bring food
to His Highness.

21:54.880 --> 21:57.540
You are here to throw yourself at me,
aren't you?

21:58.030 --> 21:58.680
No.

21:59.400 --> 22:01.260
You are here to ruin my grand plan.

22:03.350 --> 22:05.680
Let me go! I am Princess Pingning!

22:06.000 --> 22:08.270
Aren't you just a maid
from the Empress Dowager's palace?

22:08.270 --> 22:10.920
If I strangle you right now,

22:11.200 --> 22:14.260
would the Empress Dowager
ruin the peace talks for you?

22:14.960 --> 22:18.830
I have heard that the Eagle King of Northern Qin
has unmatched martial arts skills.

22:18.830 --> 22:21.880
If you win the competition
through such despicable means,

22:21.880 --> 22:23.400
history will record this,

22:23.510 --> 22:24.910
and you will be despised.

22:25.160 --> 22:26.590
Beg me to let you go first.

22:26.790 --> 22:27.830
No way!

22:28.200 --> 22:29.200
The arrow is broken.

22:29.200 --> 22:30.160
You won't win.

22:34.750 --> 22:35.680
I didn't expect

22:35.790 --> 22:37.480
the weak and useless Prince Qi

22:37.590 --> 22:38.640
to have such a

22:38.640 --> 22:39.880
courageous sister.

22:41.680 --> 22:42.480
Interesting.

22:43.640 --> 22:45.200
Are you going to kill me or not?

22:45.200 --> 22:47.070
If not, I'm leaving.

23:10.110 --> 23:11.110
Hurry up! Hold on!

23:11.440 --> 23:12.070
Hold on!

23:17.960 --> 23:21.070
Your Majesty, I have sent
many people to search for him.

23:21.270 --> 23:22.270
At Honglu Temple,

23:22.270 --> 23:24.270
we only saw those rioting students,

23:24.480 --> 23:26.070
but we didn't see Young Lord Xiao.

23:26.070 --> 23:28.240
And no one knows where Young Lord Xiao

23:28.240 --> 23:29.270
went.

23:32.590 --> 23:34.360
Your Majesty, I cannot accept a draw.

23:34.360 --> 23:35.270
If we can't find Young Lord Xiao,

23:35.270 --> 23:36.510
we will fight
the Northern Qin people to the death.

23:36.510 --> 23:37.240
Who dares?

23:38.480 --> 23:40.240
You want to clash directly
with Northern Qin's forces?

23:40.240 --> 23:42.100
Do you still want the peace talks?

23:42.200 --> 23:44.070
It was agreed that the match would
decide the fate of three border states.

23:44.070 --> 23:45.200
If we break the treaty ourselves,

23:45.200 --> 23:46.860
where is the dignity of our Ye?

23:48.310 --> 23:50.910
Your Majesty,
are we just going to endure this?

23:50.960 --> 23:52.000
We tried our best,

23:52.000 --> 23:53.460
but it only ended in a draw.

23:55.270 --> 23:56.400
For this situation,

23:57.030 --> 23:59.030
isn't Xiao Wuyi asking for it?

24:00.160 --> 24:02.960
He pushed the peace talks
despite public opinion,

24:02.960 --> 24:04.240
accepted today's battle,

24:04.240 --> 24:05.400
and then ran away without permission,

24:05.400 --> 24:06.880
leaving this mess to me

24:06.880 --> 24:08.140
and all the ministers.

24:08.200 --> 24:09.240
Such trash

24:09.480 --> 24:12.070
still wants to promote
the Beifu Restructuring?

24:12.070 --> 24:13.350
Wishful thinking.

24:13.590 --> 24:15.320
Xiao Wuyi would never run away.

24:16.200 --> 24:18.070
He Tian, send more people
to search for him.

24:18.070 --> 24:19.670
We must find Young Lord Xiao.

24:20.680 --> 24:21.540
Today's battle

24:21.790 --> 24:23.520
is to protect the dignity of Ye.

24:23.550 --> 24:25.080
Your Majesty can sit still,

24:25.240 --> 24:26.270
but I cannot.

24:29.440 --> 24:30.270
Sons of Ye,

24:30.960 --> 24:32.290
those who dare to fight,

24:32.550 --> 24:33.350
follow me!

24:33.480 --> 24:34.540
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

24:36.550 --> 24:37.610
We are not open yet.

24:40.960 --> 24:42.510
Three taels of chrysanthemum.

24:42.510 --> 24:45.170
Two catties of
sweet bamboo shoots are missing.

24:46.750 --> 24:47.880
Greetings, My Lord.

24:49.110 --> 24:51.160
The 36 secret agents in Jiankang City

24:51.160 --> 24:52.110
are all here today.

24:52.110 --> 24:53.510
Once the Eagle King wins,

24:53.640 --> 24:55.830
we'll distribute the newly written stories

24:55.830 --> 24:57.230
to all major bookstores.

24:57.270 --> 25:01.270
I guarantee it will disrupt the morale
of Southern Ye within three days.

25:01.550 --> 25:02.400
This is the draft.

25:02.400 --> 25:03.930
Please take a look, My Lord.

25:08.210 --> 25:10.100
Why is Xiao Wuyi covered in sores

25:10.720 --> 25:12.180
and sporting a full beard?

25:12.350 --> 25:14.720
These eyes, this nose...

25:16.310 --> 25:17.830
Which artist drew this?

25:18.440 --> 25:19.570
Who exactly are you?

25:22.920 --> 25:23.920
Take a good look.

25:24.440 --> 25:25.960
You drew me way too ugly.

25:26.310 --> 25:28.110
You are the legendary Xiao Wuyi?

25:28.680 --> 25:29.540
Over the years,

25:30.030 --> 25:31.270
the rumors about the Beifu Army—
looting, raping,

25:31.270 --> 25:33.510
using war for merit, destroying fields,
and massacring cities

25:33.510 --> 25:35.510
as well as classified military intelligence
from the court

25:35.510 --> 25:38.240
and information from spies
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

25:38.240 --> 25:40.300
were all spread by you, weren't they?

25:40.510 --> 25:41.510
I'll kill you!

25:44.110 --> 25:44.970
Your Highness,

25:45.720 --> 25:47.550
the vegetable market is under control.

25:47.550 --> 25:50.200
The scholars have been safely evacuated
from the Honglu Temple.

25:50.200 --> 25:50.880
However,

25:51.200 --> 25:52.720
news just came from
the martial arts arena.

25:52.720 --> 25:53.440
Da was shot.

25:53.880 --> 25:55.750
Young Master Yao
traded his life for another.

25:55.750 --> 25:57.400
He fought with the Eagle King
on horseback, fell off,

25:57.400 --> 25:58.790
and was severely injured.

25:58.790 --> 26:01.830
Prince Qi is sending people everywhere
to look for you.

26:01.830 --> 26:03.350
How is the public sentiment?

26:03.350 --> 26:04.350
They are furious

26:04.400 --> 26:07.230
and completely unwilling to reconcile
with Northern Qin.

26:07.230 --> 26:09.230
This is exactly the effect I wanted.

26:10.070 --> 26:10.720
Let's go.

26:11.350 --> 26:12.270
Avenge Yao.

26:14.270 --> 26:15.070
Eagle King,

26:16.000 --> 26:17.330
I will compete with you.

26:42.280 --> 26:45.480
Xiao Wuyi, you sure have a tough life.

26:43.420 --> 26:47.330
♪ This burning heart of mine ♪

26:48.160 --> 26:50.160
♪ Holds a soul sincere and true ♪

26:50.350 --> 26:54.640
♪ May my lifelong devotion
not be in vain ♪

26:54.660 --> 26:58.470
♪ With a fearless hand, I rise ♪

26:59.420 --> 27:01.490
♪ Stirring winds and clouds ♪

27:01.520 --> 27:04.420
♪ My heart vast as the sky ♪

27:04.440 --> 27:07.730
♪ My vow shall never fade ♪

27:07.750 --> 27:12.490
♪ I guard my fate, never forgetting ♪

27:10.240 --> 27:11.040
Your Majesty,

27:11.480 --> 27:12.680
Prince Qi,

27:13.160 --> 27:17.000
♪ With my soul, I bare my heart and roar ♪

27:13.400 --> 27:14.720
I have thoroughly searched Jiankang.

27:14.720 --> 27:17.250
All 36 secret agents of
Northern Qin are here.

27:17.330 --> 27:21.610
♪ Fight and let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

27:19.270 --> 27:21.310
Please count them, Eagle King,

27:21.890 --> 27:25.070
♪ Still hot-blooded ♪

27:22.070 --> 27:23.600
to see if anyone is missing.

27:25.620 --> 27:28.420
♪ My heart stays true ♪

27:25.640 --> 27:28.040
The day the Eagle King
arrived in Jiankang,

27:28.200 --> 27:29.830
he gave Ye a generous gift.

27:28.490 --> 27:33.070
♪ Fight to the bitter end ♪

27:30.270 --> 27:31.720
It was very impressive.

27:32.240 --> 27:33.960
Today's gift is a gesture of reciprocity.

27:33.110 --> 27:36.210
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

27:34.750 --> 27:36.400
I wonder if you are satisfied.

27:36.400 --> 27:41.480
Xiao Wuyi!

27:36.930 --> 27:42.160
♪ I dare you ♪

27:41.920 --> 27:43.680
I have another piece of news for you.

27:43.680 --> 27:44.350
Five days ago,

27:44.270 --> 27:49.080
♪ May the land know peace ♪

27:44.550 --> 27:46.410
the Hexi General of Northern Qin,

27:46.830 --> 27:48.090
Zhai Shang, rebelled.

27:48.320 --> 27:49.590
You did all that!

27:49.790 --> 27:50.640
Naturally, it was me.

27:49.850 --> 28:00.430
♪ Eternal peace ♪

27:51.160 --> 27:53.590
I heard Zhai Shang
is very interested in Yanshan,

27:53.590 --> 27:55.370
so I sent him a terrain map.

27:56.480 --> 27:57.400
If your Northern Qin

27:57.400 --> 27:59.000
refuses to sit down and talk,

27:59.440 --> 28:01.770
you will definitely face a two-front war.

28:01.880 --> 28:03.680
My Beifu soldiers can handle it.

28:02.610 --> 28:06.890
♪ Fight and let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

28:06.030 --> 28:06.720
Mulian Yu,

28:07.170 --> 28:10.270
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

28:07.880 --> 28:08.920
today, for the three prefectures,

28:08.920 --> 28:10.250
we must decide a winner.

28:10.350 --> 28:11.750
Let's have a tiebreaker.

28:12.510 --> 28:13.110
How about it?

28:12.790 --> 28:16.610
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

28:13.680 --> 28:15.540
I've been waiting for a long time!

28:32.110 --> 28:33.000
Xiao Wuyi,

28:33.830 --> 28:36.230
let's decide life and death
with one arrow.

29:07.440 --> 29:08.400
You can't see?

29:17.110 --> 29:17.910
Wait a minute.

29:22.350 --> 29:23.000
Xiao Wuyi,

29:23.680 --> 29:26.640
the Eagle King has already participated in
one round of competition.

29:26.640 --> 29:28.270
He has already used up his strength.

29:28.270 --> 29:29.590
If you compete like this,

29:29.590 --> 29:30.910
it will be too unfair.

29:31.790 --> 29:33.650
If we win under these conditions,

29:33.910 --> 29:36.040
Northern Qin will refuse to accept it.

29:41.070 --> 29:41.680
Xiao Wuyi,

29:42.440 --> 29:44.240
put your life in my hands.

29:44.830 --> 29:45.550
Do you dare?

29:46.750 --> 29:47.920
Think carefully.

29:48.680 --> 29:50.300
This poison is lethal.

29:57.310 --> 29:57.880
Come!

30:08.440 --> 30:11.170
♪ One glance stirs heart's doom,
near yet far ♪

30:11.390 --> 30:13.940
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

30:15.640 --> 30:19.650
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

30:19.820 --> 30:21.820
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

30:23.780 --> 30:26.780
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

30:27.190 --> 30:31.560
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

30:32.150 --> 30:35.060
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

30:35.820 --> 30:39.160
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

30:40.360 --> 30:44.700
♪ You know me and decided to
live and die together ♪

30:44.720 --> 30:48.380
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

30:44.750 --> 30:46.590
Sometimes, being unable to see

30:47.270 --> 30:48.930
gives you more courage than
being able to see.

30:48.930 --> 30:52.710
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

30:52.440 --> 30:54.440
Danger on the right, go left!

30:53.230 --> 30:57.340
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

30:57.420 --> 31:01.400
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

30:59.000 --> 30:59.790
Keep going!

31:01.420 --> 31:05.360
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

31:03.510 --> 31:04.110
Shoot!

31:55.900 --> 31:57.500
Danger on the left, go right!

32:08.290 --> 32:09.060
Shoot!

32:29.410 --> 32:30.130
Shoot!

32:35.590 --> 32:36.650
Danger on the left!

32:36.680 --> 32:37.680
This again?

32:41.880 --> 32:42.680
Xie Jiayu!

32:43.030 --> 32:45.030
Your commands almost got me killed.

32:45.270 --> 32:47.200
All you can do is move forward,
never stepping back

32:47.200 --> 32:48.000
or dodging.

32:48.720 --> 32:49.400
Exactly.

32:49.680 --> 32:51.240
The Beifu Army must forge ahead bravely,

32:51.240 --> 32:53.100
crushing everything in its path.

33:05.000 --> 33:06.240
Good!

33:06.240 --> 33:11.200
Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi!

33:11.200 --> 33:11.750
Wuyi!

33:13.120 --> 33:13.640
He won.

33:44.400 --> 33:45.510
They cheated.

34:10.590 --> 34:12.550
Good, we won!

34:12.550 --> 34:16.920
Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi!

34:38.480 --> 34:43.110
♪ Hear the heartbeat by my side ♪

34:39.960 --> 34:41.560
The Eagle King went for the kill

34:41.560 --> 34:43.090
because he wanted me to die.

34:43.280 --> 34:44.480
But for the peace talks to succeed,

34:43.580 --> 34:49.610
♪ Like your rush of passion toward me ♪

34:44.800 --> 34:45.929
I couldn't kill him.

34:47.030 --> 34:48.230
This won't kill him.

34:48.590 --> 34:50.880
It'll just make him suffer for a few days.

34:49.920 --> 34:54.370
♪ If you could fill the empty spaces in my memories ♪

34:55.050 --> 34:57.270
♪ Only you would stay with me ♪

34:57.290 --> 35:00.530
♪ My heartbeat will never fade ♪

35:00.730 --> 35:03.840
♪ If I could ask for one blessing ♪

35:03.860 --> 35:06.270
♪ With all the longing I hold ♪

35:06.290 --> 35:09.100
♪ It leads me back to you again ♪

35:09.120 --> 35:12.140
♪ With you as my way,
no distance is too far ♪

35:12.160 --> 35:15.050
♪ The wishes left unsaid ♪

35:13.590 --> 36:10.670
Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi! Xiao Wuyi!

35:15.080 --> 35:17.800
♪ A love I can't let go ♪

35:18.170 --> 35:20.810
♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

35:20.850 --> 35:24.100
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

35:24.300 --> 35:27.880
♪ To make it come true ♪

35:37.800 --> 35:42.870
♪ If only I could fill the empty spaces
in my memories ♪

35:43.270 --> 35:45.590
♪ Only you would stay with me ♪

35:45.910 --> 35:49.240
♪ My heartbeat will never fade ♪

35:49.270 --> 35:51.960
♪ The wishes left unsaid ♪

35:51.990 --> 35:55.060
♪ A love I can't let go ♪

35:55.080 --> 35:57.550
♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

35:57.580 --> 36:00.800
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

36:00.830 --> 36:05.290
♪ To make it come true ♪

36:18.480 --> 36:21.110
[Spirit Tablet of Duan Ying, Late Husband
of the White Horse Battalion, Beifu Army]

36:33.360 --> 36:35.780
[To Mother, Respectfully from
Your Son Xiao Wuyi]

36:52.930 --> 36:56.030
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

37:04.480 --> 37:06.880
His Majesty says you are a hero to Ye,

37:07.670 --> 37:10.840
and a benefactor to the people
of the three northern prefectures.

37:10.840 --> 37:12.570
You can have whatever you want.

37:17.590 --> 37:20.390
Young Lord Xiao,
the imperial doctor has arrived.

37:21.720 --> 37:23.620
I'm fine. I'm very...

37:24.120 --> 37:24.670
Yao.

37:24.800 --> 37:27.530
Yao, stop talking
if you want to recover quickly.

37:29.000 --> 37:30.110
Don't be mad.

37:32.190 --> 37:34.400
Please apply the medicine
and acupuncture to Yao immediately.

37:34.400 --> 37:35.150
-Yes.
-Yes.

37:38.030 --> 37:38.920
Tell Mother

37:39.420 --> 37:40.420
not to blame Wuyi.

37:41.360 --> 37:42.560
I'm very happy today.

37:48.000 --> 37:49.330
What did the doctor say?

37:49.400 --> 37:50.400
He is very strong.

37:50.670 --> 37:51.880
He endured the pain

37:52.380 --> 37:54.900
and refused to show it in front of us.

37:56.960 --> 37:59.440
But all his internal organs are injured.

37:59.960 --> 38:01.890
He'll need to rest well for a while.

38:02.800 --> 38:04.670
It's my fault for returning too late.

38:04.670 --> 38:06.030
You don't need to blame yourself.

38:06.030 --> 38:07.360
Yao is very happy today.

38:07.510 --> 38:09.840
At least he proved to everyone

38:10.760 --> 38:12.480
that the Prince Jing'an's Mansion

38:12.480 --> 38:14.610
is not represented by Xiao Wuyi alone.

38:51.360 --> 38:52.070
Mother.

38:52.630 --> 38:53.190
I...

38:54.360 --> 38:55.190
Let me see.

39:08.630 --> 39:09.360
Does it hurt?

39:11.230 --> 39:12.070
Jiayu said

39:13.070 --> 39:16.670
a child who doesn't cry out in pain
isn't necessarily pain-free.

39:38.670 --> 39:39.360
Yaoyao,

39:40.670 --> 39:41.440
what is that?

39:43.670 --> 39:46.230
I've been learning lightness skills
from Yan Yue lately.

39:46.230 --> 39:48.070
Every morning I wear these sandbags

39:48.070 --> 39:50.000
to train at the martial arts arena.

39:50.590 --> 39:52.250
But you used to be the laziest,

39:52.400 --> 39:53.880
and you hated getting hurt.

39:53.880 --> 39:55.540
It's all because of Xiao Wuyi.

39:55.730 --> 39:57.590
Last time he left me stranded
at the Honglu Temple.

39:57.590 --> 39:59.650
It took me a whole night to climb down.

40:01.510 --> 40:03.310
But he was right about one thing.

40:03.480 --> 40:04.670
If you want to play with fire,

40:04.670 --> 40:06.230
you have to learn how to escape first.

40:06.230 --> 40:07.880
Since I want to travel the world,

40:07.880 --> 40:09.080
I not only need money,

40:09.230 --> 40:11.760
but also some martial arts
to protect myself.

40:14.480 --> 40:15.360
Silly.

40:16.190 --> 40:17.250
I will protect you.

40:17.280 --> 40:19.000
You don't need to learn these things.

40:19.000 --> 40:20.530
And I won't let you get hurt.

40:20.550 --> 40:21.680
How could that work?

40:22.030 --> 40:23.670
I have to rely on myself
when I'm away from home.

40:23.670 --> 40:25.670
How can I rely on you for everything?

40:28.000 --> 40:29.060
Today, you and Wuyi

40:29.230 --> 40:30.890
worked really well together.

40:31.280 --> 40:33.400
I didn't expect you to learn
how to use war drums.

40:33.400 --> 40:35.360
You gave him that sleeve arrow too, right?

40:35.360 --> 40:36.590
Yes. How was it?

40:36.590 --> 40:38.050
Didn't I look impressive?

40:38.360 --> 40:40.820
Not to mention my excellent craftsmanship.

40:42.280 --> 40:43.680
Today was so satisfying.

40:45.440 --> 40:46.760
But you always used to say

40:46.760 --> 40:48.550
that battlefields are lawless,

40:48.550 --> 40:49.840
and that you hated killing the most.

40:49.840 --> 40:51.840
Isn't peace the most important thing?

40:51.840 --> 40:53.510
But the Eagle King brought the fight
to our doorstep.

40:53.510 --> 40:54.920
How could I tolerate that?

40:54.920 --> 40:56.670
Besides, the day the Eagle King
entered the city,

40:56.670 --> 40:59.130
weren't you and the students
indignant too?

40:59.300 --> 41:00.480
Fortunately, today,

41:00.480 --> 41:02.280
Xiao Wuyi rooted out
the Northern Qin spies,

41:02.280 --> 41:03.800
reclaimed the three prefectures,

41:03.800 --> 41:05.000
and vented our anger.

41:06.230 --> 41:08.630
Sometimes fists really are the only truth.

41:09.000 --> 41:10.530
That saying is really true.

41:10.760 --> 41:13.110
I even designed a sword for Xiao Wuyi,

41:13.440 --> 41:15.630
one no less impressive
than the Longque Blade.

41:15.630 --> 41:16.550
A man like him

41:17.110 --> 41:19.170
deserves the best sword in the world.

41:20.550 --> 41:21.550
But don't you feel

41:22.280 --> 41:23.320
today all of us

41:23.320 --> 41:24.440
were used by Wuyi?

41:25.150 --> 41:27.360
In this battle, he not only won back
the three prefectures,

41:27.360 --> 41:28.960
but the prestige
he gained from turning the tide

41:28.960 --> 41:31.800
also laid the foundation for his future reform
of the Northern Prefecture.

41:31.800 --> 41:33.440
He was the one who sought peace talks,

41:33.440 --> 41:35.900
and he is the one
who won the people's hearts.

41:36.920 --> 41:39.000
But is there anything wrong with that?

41:39.000 --> 41:41.600
A person with the ability
and will to protect Ye

41:41.800 --> 41:43.200
deserves such prestige.

41:45.360 --> 41:46.110
I thought

41:46.630 --> 41:49.230
you liked people
who stay aloof from the world.

41:50.550 --> 41:52.550
I do like staying aloof from the world,

41:52.550 --> 41:54.030
but I can choose not to fight

41:54.030 --> 41:56.490
because someone
is already fighting for me.

41:59.590 --> 42:00.480
Then what if

42:02.840 --> 42:03.760
I want to fight too?
